Date: Sat, 11 Apr 2026 18:52:24 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] feat(observability): diagnostics + CI suite for Cowork
 capabilities

- filePreviewService: in-memory docx diagnostic counters
  (docxPrimary/docxOfficeParser/docxJszip/docxDegraded + lastError).
  Replaces loose console.warn with structured JSON log lines
  ([filePreview.docx] stage_failed) so we can grep production logs
  to see exactly which fallback stage is handling real-world docx.
  Exposes getFilePreviewDiagnostics() for an ops route.

- New workflow: .github/workflows/cowork-capabilities.yml runs the
  9520-test offline capability suite on every PR that touches
  cowork_test_suite/ or the files it exercises. Installs deterministic
  pinned deps (python-docx, openpyxl, python-pptx, reportlab, pypdf,
  mammoth, matplotlib, markdown2, pillow), runs pytest with JUnit XML,
  uploads results + generated artifacts. Fits in 20 minutes.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
